            "key": "signature",
            "value": "{{verification_signature}}"
          },
          {
            "key": "expires",
            "value": "{{verification_expires}}"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": "Verify a central user's email address using a signed verification URL.\n\n**Auth:** requires authenticated central session/token (`auth:central-api`).\n\n**Path params:**\n- `verification_id`: central user id\n- `verification_hash`: `sha1(user_email)`\n\n**Query params:**\n- `signature` (required): signed URL signature\n- `expires` (required): signed URL expiration timestamp\n\n**Behavior:**\n- Validates the signed URL (`signed` middleware)\n- Loads the user by `verification_id`\n- Validates `verification_hash` against the user's email\n- Marks email as verified and dispatches verification event on success\n- Returns validation errors when the hash is invalid or email is already verified"
    },
